  "description": "Pure tonal percussion — every voice pitched far above the standard drum range. Voices v6, v7, v8 become glockenspiel-adjacent metallic tones. No kick identity. No snare. A shower of pitched transients where the rain is made of glass. MUTATE applies micro-detuning between hits for cloud resonance.",
